{"tid":1812083,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如今利物浦雖強！名宿：但還比不上08年那支紅魔","createTime":"2020-01-05T08:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T08:29:29.000Z","uid":147522,"like":26,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"1a75c0d556975f441704369c338bdef643300889","tid":1812083,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:48:57.000Z","msg":"　　曼聯昔日著名中堅里奧費迪南稱，如今的利物浦雖然很強，但還無法和2008年的曼聯相提並論，真要想比較，紅軍需要先拿兩次背靠背的聯賽冠軍再說。<br />\n<br />\n　　高普的球隊上季拿到了歐聯冠軍，今季奪得英超的希望很大。在Twitter上，當被問到如今的紅軍和2008年的曼聯誰高誰下時，費迪南回答說：「先需要連續拿兩年英超冠軍，然後才可以比較（08年的曼聯）。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　「不過無可否認的是，他們正在成為一支偉大球隊的道路上。」<br />\n<br />\n　　2008年的那支曼聯，擁有C.朗拿度、朗尼、泰維斯、里奧-費迪南等一批名將，不僅拿到了2007/08賽季的歐聯冠軍，還在英超中實現了三連冠（2007、2008、2009）。"},{"pid":"458ac72d18a920af22e77dc87ccfcacb472e2109","tid":1812083,"uid":64484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:53:17.000Z","msg":"08年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d9abf1f1e2506a857513f2bddcba483f3c0270","tid":1812083,"uid":42409,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T09:00:33.000Z","msg":"想知當年幾多分就拎到英超"},{"pid":"df4f8063007e51c06fe01bb32c23933e801407f2","tid":1812083,"uid":234553,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T09:11:27.000Z","msg":"睇錯支那紅魔"},{"pid":"a15b95f6a5c02f680b2553970175276744919100","tid":1812083,"uid":155902,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:45:20.000Z","msg":"背靠背的聯賽冠軍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41791a1e330e37bb50be9db7fcc4bfa1ef14d8f8","tid":1812083,"uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0d9abf1f1e2506a857513f2bddcba483f3c0270","tid":1812083,"uid":42409,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T09:00:33.000Z","msg":"想知當年幾多分就拎到英超"},"citedBy":0